channel.title: Would like to help code a 562 server
channel.description: hey i am getting damn bored of 317's, 97% are leeched and owned by idiots. and for the 3% it is the hardest to become popular while any dumbass can add 43594 to his router, download a pi server, advertise he has torva, nex korasi, and that bullshit and have players immediately. :eek: :confused: anyways, i am good at coding with 317s and i would like to learn to code for 562, so if anyone has a 562 server they need help with i can do basic things i will learn quickly. i am not the guy you are looking for if you have serious problems with your server but if you don't have time to add everything or whatever the situation may be i can assist you for free, i just want to learn more about rsps and java. there is no catch or anything, i do not expect anything in return, i do not care about a staff position, donations, or anything.
